      <div class="sim-subhead sim-subhead--gap"><span class="sim-subhead-dot"></span>Isi <code>satusehat_log</code> (master) — {masterRows.length} baris, kolom sama persis dengan DDL</div>
      <div class="sim-table-wrap">
        <table class="sim-table" style="min-width:1680px;">
          <thead><tr>
            <th style="width:30px;">id</th>
            <th style="width:70px;">module</th>
            <th style="width:130px;">resource_type</th>
            <th style="width:90px;">noreg</th>
            <th style="width:120px;">source_table</th>
            <th style="width:90px;">source_id</th>
            <th style="width:120px;">observation_code</th>
            <th style="width:120px;">encounter_status</th>
            <th style="width:60px;">status</th>
            <th style="width:140px;">ihs_id</th>
            <th style="width:54px;">retry_count</th>
            <th style="width:150px;">last_error</th>
            <th style="width:92px;">sent_at</th>
            <th style="width:92px;">created_at</th>
            <th style="width:92px;">updated_at</th>
          </tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {masterRows.map((r) => {
              const meta = sourceMeta(r);
              const attempts = detailRows.filter((d) => d.log === r.id);
              const retryCount = Math.max(0, attempts.length - 1);
              const lastErr = attempts.find((a) => a.err)?.err || null;
              return (
                <tr>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{r.id}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">ranap</td>
                  <td>{r.type}</td>
                  <td class={r.noreg ? 'sim-mono sim-info' : 'sim-mono'}>{r.noreg || 'NULL'}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{meta.table}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{meta.id}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{r.obs}</td>
                  <td>{r.enc}</td>
                  <td><span class="sim-pill sim-pill--sent">sent</span></td>
                  <td class="sim-mono sim-ihs">{r.ihs}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{retryCount}</td>
                  <td class={lastErr ? 'sim-bad-txt' : 'sim-mono'}>{lastErr || 'NULL'}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{r.sent}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{r.created}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{r.sent}</td>
                </tr>
              );
            })}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="sim-subhead sim-subhead--gap"><span class="sim-subhead-dot sim-subhead-dot--accent"></span>Isi <code>satusehat_log_detail</code> — {detailRows.length} baris, kolom sama persis dengan DDL (JSON dipadatkan)</div>
      <div class="sim-table-wrap">
        <table class="sim-table" style="min-width:1820px;">
          <thead><tr>
            <th style="width:26px;">id</th>
            <th style="width:50px;">log_id</th>
            <th style="width:90px;">noreg</th>
            <th style="width:54px;">attempt_no</th>
            <th style="width:80px;">http_method</th>
            <th style="width:170px;">endpoint</th>
            <th style="width:240px;">request_body</th>
            <th style="width:100px;">response_status</th>
            <th style="width:220px;">response_body</th>
            <th style="width:170px;">error_message</th>
            <th style="width:90px;">duration_ms</th>
            <th style="width:185px;">triggered_by</th>
            <th style="width:92px;">created_at</th>
          </tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {detailRows.map((d) => {
              const ok = d.st >= 200 && d.st < 300;
              const rowClass = !ok ? 'sim-row-fail' : d.att > 1 ? 'sim-row-ok' : '';
              const dnoreg = masterRows.find((m) => m.id === d.log)?.noreg;
              return (
                <tr class={rowClass}>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.id}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.log}</td>
                  <td class={dnoreg ? 'sim-mono sim-info' : 'sim-mono'}>{dnoreg || 'NULL'}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.att}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.m}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.ep}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono sim-json-preview">{jsonPreview(d, 'request')}</td>
                  <td class={ok ? 'sim-mono sim-ok' : 'sim-mono sim-bad'}>{d.st}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono sim-json-preview">{jsonPreview(d, 'response')}</td>
                  <td class={d.err ? 'sim-bad-txt' : ''}>{d.err || '—'}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.dur}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.by}</td>
                  <td class="sim-mono">{d.at}</td>
                </tr>
              );
            })}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="sim-subhead sim-subhead--gap"><span class="sim-subhead-dot sim-subhead-dot--accent"></span>Contoh isi kolom <code>request_body</code> &amp; <code>response_body</code></div>
      <div class="sim-payload-list" style="margin: 0 24px;">
        <article class="sim-payload-card">
          <div class="sim-payload-head">
            <div class="sim-payload-title">
              Composition — Resume Medis Rawat Inap (WAJIB, khas ranap)
              <span class="sim-mono">detail id: 31 · log_id: 30 · triggered_by: system:KirimCompositionJob · 2026-06-08 10:31</span>
              <span class="sim-payload-endpoint">POST /Composition</span>
            </div>
            <span class="sim-http sim-http--ok">201</span>
          </div>
          <div class="sim-payload-grid">
            <div class="sim-payload-pane"><div class="sim-payload-label">request_body</div><pre class="sim-payload-code">{JSON.stringify(payloadCI.request_body, null, 2)}</pre></div>
            <div class="sim-payload-pane"><div class="sim-payload-label">response_body</div><pre class="sim-payload-code">{JSON.stringify(payloadCI.response_body, null, 2)}</pre></div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="sim-payload-card">
          <div class="sim-payload-head">
            <div class="sim-payload-title">
              MedicationDispense (pemberian pagi) — attempt_no 1 — GAGAL
              <span class="sim-mono">detail id: 13 · log_id: 13 · triggered_by: system:KirimMedicationDispenseJob · 2026-06-06 10:01</span>
              <span class="sim-payload-endpoint">POST /MedicationDispense</span>
            </div>
            <span class="sim-http sim-http--err">500</span>
          </div>
          <div class="sim-payload-error"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation"></i> error_message: Internal Server Error pada SatuSehat (transient)</div>
          <div class="sim-payload-grid">
            <div class="sim-payload-pane"><div class="sim-payload-label">request_body</div><pre class="sim-payload-code">{JSON.stringify(payloadFail.request_body, null, 2)}</pre></div>
            <div class="sim-payload-pane"><div class="sim-payload-label">response_body</div><pre class="sim-payload-code">{JSON.stringify(payloadFail.response_body, null, 2)}</pre></div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="sim-payload-card">
          <div class="sim-payload-head">
            <div class="sim-payload-title">
              MedicationDispense (pemberian pagi) — attempt_no 2 — SUKSES (retry otomatis)
              <span class="sim-mono">detail id: 14 · log_id: 13 · triggered_by: system:RetryService · 2026-06-06 10:06</span>
              <span class="sim-payload-endpoint">POST /MedicationDispense</span>
            </div>
            <span class="sim-http sim-http--ok">201</span>
          </div>
          <div class="sim-payload-grid">
            <div class="sim-payload-pane"><div class="sim-payload-label">request_body</div><pre class="sim-payload-code">{JSON.stringify(payloadRetry.request_body, null, 2)}</pre></div>
            <div class="sim-payload-pane"><div class="sim-payload-label">response_body</div><pre class="sim-payload-code">{JSON.stringify(payloadRetry.response_body, null, 2)}</pre></div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="sim-subhead sim-subhead--gap"><span class="sim-subhead-dot"></span>Query yang sering dipakai</div>
      <pre class="sim-sql">{querySql}</pre>

      <div class="sim-note" style="margin: 14px 24px 10px;">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-clock" />
        <span><b>Soal <code>created_at</code>:</b> kolom ini ada di <u>kedua</u> tabel dan diisi otomatis oleh
        database (<code>DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP</code>) — Anda tidak perlu mengisinya manual. Di master ada juga
        <code>updated_at</code> (auto-update tiap status berubah) dan <code>sent_at</code> (waktu sukses terkirim),
        sedangkan tiap baris detail punya <code>created_at</code> sendiri sehingga jejak waktu per-attempt tetap akurat.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-note" style="margin: 0 24px 24px;">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield" />
        <span><b>Soal username:</b> tidak wajib, tapi <b>disarankan</b> lewat kolom <code>triggered_by</code> di
        <code>satusehat_log_detail</code>. Mayoritas attempt dipicu job otomatis (<code>system:NamaJob</code>), jadi
        username manusia sering kosong. Nilainya jadi penting saat ada <b>resend manual</b> dari dashboard —
        di situ simpan <code>user:&lt;NIP/username&gt;</code> agar jelas siapa yang menekan tombol kirim ulang.
        Identitas pasien/perawat klinis sendiri sudah tercatat di tabel sumber SIMRS (mis. <code>vitalsign.created_by</code>),
        bukan tanggung jawab tabel log ini.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>


<script>
  import '../scripts/simulasiRanap.js';
</script>
